items.sentence: I'm sure that I calculated the bill correctly.
Tom isn't Mary's ex-husband. He's her brother.
Tom isn't mopping the floor. He's sweeping it.
I haven't written Tom a letter in a long time.
I didn't think that Tom would be so depressed.
Tom was aware that Mary couldn't speak French.
I don't regret the days that I spent with Tom.
Tom's stepdaughters' names are Mary and Alice.
I think that I should organize a little party.
I returned the shirt because it was too small.
